Company Overview of Solus Alternative Asset Management L.P.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Solus Alternative Asset Management L.P. is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It invests in the public equity and alternative markets. The firm mainly invests in leveraged loans, high-yield bonds, and distressed securities to make its portfolio. Solus Alternative Asset Management is base in New York, New York.


