Solus Alternative Asset Management LP Decreased Its Visteon (VC) Position, Principal Financial Group Has Trimmed Fluor New (FLR) Stake


					
						July 25, 2017 - By Ellis Scott

Solus Alternative Asset Management Lp decreased Visteon Corp (VC) stake by 32.26% reported in 2016Q4 SEC filing. Solus Alternative Asset Management Lp sold 394,159 shares as Visteon Corp (VC)’s stock rose 9.26%. The Solus Alternative Asset Management Lp holds 827,841 shares with $66.51M value, down from 1.22M last quarter. Visteon Corp now has $3.49B valuation. The stock rose 0.69% or $0.76 reaching $110.35. About 314,621 shares traded. Visteon Corp (NYSE:VC) has risen 41.15% since July 25, 2016 and is uptrending. It has outperformed by 24.45% the S&P500.







Principal Financial Group Inc decreased Fluor Corp New (FLR) stake by 84.17% reported in 2016Q4 SEC filing. Principal Financial Group Inc sold 1.11M shares as Fluor Corp New (FLR)’s stock declined 18.75%. The Principal Financial Group Inc holds 208,452 shares with $10.95M value, down from 1.32 million last quarter. Fluor Corp New now has $6.34B valuation. The stock increased 2.15% or $0.96 during the last trading session, reaching $45.68. About 1.51M shares traded or 19.84% up from the average. Fluor Corporation (NEW) (NYSE:FLR) has declined 7.15% since July 25, 2016 and is downtrending. It has underperformed by 23.85% the S&P500.
Analysts await Visteon Corp (NYSE:VC) to report earnings on July, 27 before the open. They expect $1.24 earnings per share, up 1.64% or $0.02 from last year’s $1.22 per share. VC’s profit will be $39.22 million for 22.25 P/E if the $1.24 EPS becomes a reality. After $1.73 actual earnings per share reported by Visteon Corp for the previous quarter, Wall Street now forecasts -28.32% negative EPS growth. 
Since March 3, 2017, it had 1 insider purchase, and 1 insider sale for $406 activity. Shares for $191,393 were bought by MANZO ROBERT. $190,987 worth of Visteon Corp (NYSE:VC) was sold by Vallance Robert R.
Among 14 analysts covering Visteon (NYSE:VC), 9 have Buy rating, 0 Sell and 5 Hold. Therefore 64% are positive. Visteon had 25 analyst reports since August 28, 2015 according to SRatingsIntel. As per Tuesday, April 19, the company rating was maintained by JP Morgan. Morgan Stanley initiated the shares of VC in report on Monday, April 24 with “Equal-Weight” rating. FBR Capital maintained Visteon Corp (NYSE:VC) rating on Friday, April 29. FBR Capital has “Outperform” rating and $90 target. The stock of Visteon Corp (NYSE:VC) has “Equal-Weight” rating given on Tuesday, May 3 by Barclays Capital. The company was upgraded on Friday, May 12 by Morgan Stanley. Raymond James initiated the stock with “Market Perform” rating in Thursday, June 23 report. As per Thursday, September 17, the company rating was initiated by Wells Fargo. The stock has “Hold” rating by Deutsche Bank on Wednesday, July 20. The stock of Visteon Corp (NYSE:VC) earned “Outperform” rating by BMO Capital Markets on Monday, June 26. The stock has “Buy” rating by Goldman Sachs on Monday, April 3.
Investors sentiment decreased to 0.78 in Q4 2016. Its down 0.04, from 0.82 in 2016Q3. It dropped, as 32 investors sold VC shares while 93 reduced holdings. 45 funds opened positions while 52 raised stakes. 32.22 million shares or 6.41% less from 34.43 million shares in 2016Q3 were reported. Nomura Asset Mgmt, Japan-based fund reported 1,250 shares. Barclays Public Limited Company has invested 0% in Visteon Corp (NYSE:VC). Bogle Invest Management Limited Partnership De holds 3,459 shares. Princeton Alpha Lp reported 6,638 shares. Blackrock Fund Advsr holds 0.01% or 348,370 shares. Putnam Ltd Company holds 0.02% in Visteon Corp (NYSE:VC) or 97,809 shares. Blackrock Limited Liability stated it has 0% of its portfolio in Visteon Corp (NYSE:VC). Etrade Cap Mngmt Ltd Liability, New York-based fund reported 6,017 shares. Ajo Limited Partnership accumulated 0.19% or 578,205 shares. State Bank Of Mellon Corporation holds 0.05% of its portfolio in Visteon Corp (NYSE:VC) for 2.16M shares. Northcoast Asset Llc invested in 3,347 shares or 0.03% of the stock. Teacher Retirement System Of Texas holds 0% or 2,705 shares in its portfolio. Teachers Retirement System Of The State Of Kentucky invested in 0.02% or 22,330 shares. First Quadrant Limited Partnership Ca holds 94,273 shares. Zurcher Kantonalbank (Zurich Cantonalbank) holds 0.01% or 12,368 shares.
Since March 1, 2017, it had 0 buys, and 2 insider sales for $525,223 activity. Shares for $96,935 were sold by Chopra Robin K on Tuesday, March 14. Shares for $428,288 were sold by BARNARD RAY F. on Wednesday, March 1.
Analysts await Fluor Corporation (NEW) (NYSE:FLR) to report earnings on August, 3 after the close. They expect $0.60 EPS, down 16.67% or $0.12 from last year’s $0.72 per share. FLR’s profit will be $83.27 million for 19.03 P/E if the $0.60 EPS becomes a reality. After $0.57 actual EPS reported by Fluor Corporation (NEW) for the previous quarter, Wall Street now forecasts 5.26% EPS growth. 
Principal Financial Group Inc increased Big 5 Sporting Goods Corp (NASDAQ:BGFV) stake by 379,341 shares to 508,868 valued at $8.83M in 2016Q4. It also upped Quanta Svcs Inc (NYSE:PWR) stake by 898,662 shares and now owns 1.59M shares. Fuller H B Co (NYSE:FUL) was raised too. 
Investors sentiment decreased to 0.92 in 2016 Q4. Its down 0.10, from 1.02 in 2016Q3. It turned negative, as 50 investors sold FLR shares while 170 reduced holdings. 71 funds opened positions while 131 raised stakes. 115.00 million shares or 3.45% more from 111.16 million shares in 2016Q3 were reported. Menora Mivtachim Limited reported 190,000 shares. Proshare Advisors Ltd Llc reported 42,998 shares. Strs Ohio reported 0% in Fluor Corporation (NEW) (NYSE:FLR). Rhumbline Advisers holds 0.03% of its portfolio in Fluor Corporation (NEW) (NYSE:FLR) for 235,056 shares. Quantbot Tech Limited Partnership holds 10,773 shares. Gam Ag holds 0.05% or 53,594 shares in its portfolio. Sandy Spring Comml Bank invested in 0% or 375 shares. 337,212 are held by California Pub Employees Retirement System. Hgk Asset Mgmt owns 1.77% invested in Fluor Corporation (NEW) (NYSE:FLR) for 247,086 shares. Blackrock Fund Advsrs holds 0.03% of its portfolio in Fluor Corporation (NEW) (NYSE:FLR) for 2.61M shares. Roundview Capital Ltd Co has invested 0.42% in Fluor Corporation (NEW) (NYSE:FLR). Howe And Rusling owns 32 shares or 0% of their US portfolio. Employees Retirement Association Of Colorado reported 25,775 shares. Cantab Cap Prtnrs Limited Liability Partnership reported 0% stake. State Of Tennessee Treasury Department holds 0.02% or 84,207 shares in its portfolio.








