Our Team


Solus Alternative Asset Management has 50 employees, including 17 investment professionals. Many of our key professionals have worked together for over 10 years. Although our research analysts are divided by industry, collaboration and communication amongst our analysts, in-house bankruptcy lawyers, portfolio managers, and traders is critical to our investment process. Our Risk Management team works closely with the portfolio managers and traders on a real time basis providing reporting, analysis and systems support. In addition, Solus has robust Legal, Compliance, and Investor Relations.





